1772341858526826	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3Ag		item.comment	bn-16w3	{"body":"## Audit Results\n\n**Total**: 356 Command::new(\"git\") across 35 files in crates/\n**Production**: ~78 calls (22%)\n**Test/Setup**: ~278 calls (78%)\n\n### Production calls by crate:\n- **maw-core**: 10 (refs: 0, backend/git: 4, merge/build: 4, oplog: 2)\n- **maw-cli**: 68 (push: 17, working_copy: 22, recover: 9, transport: 9, capture: 7, v2_init: 4)\n- **maw-tui**: 5 (app.rs data fetching)\n- **maw-assurance**: 13 (oracle + trace, justified — test/verification code)\n- **maw-git**: 3 (push_impl: 2, config_impl: 1 — justified fallbacks)\n\n### Disposition:\n- **Replace**: maw-core (10) + maw-cli (68) + maw-tui (5) = 83 production calls\n- **Keep with justification**: maw-git (3, git CLI fallback for push), maw-assurance (13, verification tool)\n- **Test code**: ~278 calls — keep as-is, test setup helpers are fine with CLI"}	blake3:nMx9oLbDJAax5ZM5kmobPoQScjDF8oerS-6wKLfxBQg
