1772343586989654	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy4Ag		item.move	bn-1ekm	{"state":"doing"}	blake3:3eOfXjZp3zIwKi4JvZn8yINrMObOOuBNnf2pDUWTGk0
1772343597436018	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy4Qg		item.comment	bn-1ekm	{"body":"## Decision: Keep CLI fallback for push\n\n**Rationale:**\n1. push.rs has 17 CLI calls (push, fetch, rev-list, merge-base, ls-remote, tag)\n2. gix-protocol/gix-transport are lower-level than needed — would require significant wrapper code\n3. Push is network-bound; subprocess overhead is negligible\n4. Push path is cleanly isolated in push.rs and transport.rs\n5. transport.rs already has TODO(gix) annotations for the remaining 3-4 CLI calls (push/fetch)\n\n**Action:**\n- Keep Command::new(\"git\") push/fetch/ls-remote calls as permanent CLI fallbacks\n- Document in maw-git that push/fetch operations delegate to CLI\n- All non-push CLI calls already replaced by maw-git trait methods"}	blake3:RiJyQnaNDPiQDBehl4HCEHg68mFBaveeXii-ify6wo8
1772343600669717	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy4gg		item.move	bn-1ekm	{"state":"done"}	blake3:paTH3Suxur22gqoq1q1bDMepZ1ov4kAxOR_nvDuY_GA
