1772343757350349	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy5gg		item.move	bn-2fv3	{"state":"doing"}	blake3:DHITs5_5Ckl-k5YvMfnwUnoihY-yVgSqE3M83yoWyEU
1772343765866187	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy5wg		item.comment	bn-2fv3	{"body":"## Ready for publish\n\nBoth crates are publish-ready:\n\n### maw-git (publish first)\n```bash\ncargo publish -p maw-git\n```\n- Dry-run succeeded, 19 files, 163KB packaged\n- All metadata present: description, license, repository, keywords\n\n### maw-core (publish second, after maw-git is on crates.io)\n```bash\ncargo publish -p maw-core\n```\n- Depends on maw-git = \"0.49.0\"\n- Dry-run validates structure but can't resolve maw-git until it's published\n\n### Publish order\n1. `cargo publish -p maw-git` (no dependencies on local crates)\n2. Wait for crates.io index to update (~2-5 minutes)\n3. `cargo publish -p maw-core` (depends on maw-git 0.49.0)\n\n### Note\nRequires crates.io authentication. This step requires explicit user authorization."}	blake3:3nzBvShNfQHNhWIFAAwU3VaF0-RcfzRGnJx7WlESb_8
1772343769735876	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy6Ag		item.move	bn-2fv3	{"state":"done"}	blake3:iUJT2hwSpi3uMQBc5y7XxDEfFD4hlJ33t7oiiRa-XfY
1772343777010773	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy6Qg		item.move	bn-3cck	{"state":"doing"}	blake3:S8ALh2UmgN2kzU4Kzo9qM5y3aOBN7LkWE3Im4yHt0y4
1772343777041253	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy6gg		item.comment	bn-3cck	{"body":"## Deferred — depends on actual publish\n\nAfter maw-git and maw-core are published to crates.io, update root Cargo.toml:\n\n```toml\n# Change from path-only to path+version:\nmaw-core = { path = \"crates/maw-core\", version = \"0.49.0\" }\nmaw-git = { path = \"crates/maw-git\", version = \"0.49.0\" }\n```\n\nAnd in maw-cli Cargo.toml:\n```toml\nmaw-core = { path = \"../maw-core\", version = \"0.49.0\" }\nmaw-git = { path = \"../maw-git\", version = \"0.49.0\" }\n```\n\nThis allows downstream consumers to use the crates from crates.io while the workspace still uses local paths for development."}	blake3:UkYPFAYotrOusbwlEKJiXKA25jWFyP2-QwkkYGR10FY
