1772348978896444	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7Qg		item.create	bn-1u5k	{"description":"File: crates/maw-git/src/refs_impl.rs:59-68. delete_ref returns NotFound when ref doesnt exist, but trait doc says No-op if not found. Fix: return Ok(()) when try_find_reference returns None.","kind":"bug","labels":["review-finding"],"title":"[P0] delete_ref errors on missing ref, violates idempotent contract"}	blake3:VqNhZVjHuvmfkiC1faRaYoK2VWy52oZ4C7K5fpmMKDY
1772348980517188	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7gg		item.create	bn-1ga3	{"description":"File: crates/maw-git/src/checkout_impl.rs:12-94. gix checkout only writes files from tree, doesn't remove pre-existing files absent from tree. Trait doc says existing files not in tree are removed. Fix: enumerate workdir before checkout, remove stale files after.","kind":"bug","labels":["review-finding"],"title":"[P0] checkout_tree does not remove stale files from workdir"}	blake3:GApB7pZmeYblo9wO-hMniH0GTZhWz60PmG3xUVgjMmQ
1772348982504706	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7wg		item.create	bn-1usu	{"description":"Files: stash_impl.rs:299, worktree_impl.rs:20. Unvalidated paths from tree objects/worktree names could write outside intended dirs via .. components. Fix: validate no .. in path components.","kind":"bug","labels":["review-finding","security"],"title":"[P0] path traversal in stash_apply and worktree_add"}	blake3:b_Yhb7lO_2gnH8byz9PmW6wldcJzw5Q-mNs6zinGVYo
