1772348997744198	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy8wg		item.create	bn-i6hv	{"description":"File: crates/maw-tui/src/lib.rs:21-43. No panic hook or RAII guard for terminal restore. If app.run() panics after enable_raw_mode(), terminal is left in raw mode. Fix: install panic hook that calls disable_raw_mode + LeaveAlternateScreen.","kind":"bug","labels":["review-finding"],"title":"[P1] TUI terminal cleanup not guaranteed on panic"}	blake3:1SnzGZ5iiXoQ4ru9dIElDtX9xlNCuwvwUCeCib1lgaE
