1772349516721855	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy_gg		item.comment	bn-2bcd	{"body":"False positive. Verified: Region::Lines uses exclusive end (documented in conflict.rs:124 as 'One past the last line'). region_byte_range correctly uses line_starts[end-1] which gives the start of the exclusive-end line, i.e., one past the last included line. Traced through concrete examples and all byte ranges are correct."}	blake3:c-1V-Tx6_zn7vUkQFd-vbJlhM4Ex1XwG_IGbkIILc5E
