1772390364893505	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEypgk		item.move	bn-onw5	{"state":"done"}	blake3:gqJYI63ybp1uzvOp8_Xl3QrvSgqPccUeDP3um2jgq6g
