1772469312207735	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEyAg		item.create	bn-1vbt	{"description":"Current merge success output prints a soft hint ('To amend ...') when --message is omitted, and agents often leave generic 'epoch: merge ...' subjects. Strengthen this UX so agents reliably amend before push.\n\nScope:\n- In text output, upgrade from soft hint to stronger warning/recommendation language (action-first, explicit risk of generic message).\n- Keep a copy-paste command to amend.\n- In JSON output, populate the  field per CLI conventions with machine-readable guidance when auto-generated subject is used.\n\nAcceptance:\n- Running merge without --message clearly signals this requires follow-up.\n- JSON output includes  guidance instead of burying this in free-form message text.\n- Spelling uses  consistently.","kind":"task","title":"Strengthen merge message guidance for agents"}	blake3:N0srWTgOYI-r2RqyaIsUMSZewN16qr5lK2HF4lW5Rhw
1772469321849035	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEyAw		item.comment	bn-1vbt	{"body":"Clarification/correction: JSON output must populate the 'advice' field (per CLI conventions doc), and text should use 'amend' spelling consistently. Preferred UX: strong WARNING/IMPORTANT style guidance plus explicit amend command when merge auto-generates commit subject."}	blake3:j44wMQSiB5wCip-6TFp0h1fGdj11ReF1u0fSG0Rxnfs
1772469574154265	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEyBA		item.comment	bn-1vbt	{"body":"Implemented in maw ws merge: stronger text guidance when --message is omitted (WARNING + IMPORTANT + explicit amend command), and JSON success output now includes an advice entry with type 'generic-merge-message' plus details (commit_subject, amend_command). Added tests in tests/merge.rs and merge.rs unit tests for advice presence and guidance output."}	blake3:f4ccWfWakwV7cdrMyCnmbULB3No8nzYl2-uo1xTt2zo
