1772759942969403	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEyZw		item.comment	bn-1mvj	{"body":"Implemented `maw changes close` behavior in crates/maw-cli/src/changes/mod.rs: loads active change record from store, checks linked workspaces unless --force, verifies PR merged (using stored state or gh pr view), archives metadata via changes store lock + archive move, clears index mappings, and optionally deletes local/remote change branches with trunk-protection guardrails. Added JSON/text close output envelope and actionable error messages. Verified with cargo fmt, cargo test -p maw-cli changes_subcommand_is_registered, cargo test -p maw-cli changes::store::tests, and cargo run -p maw-cli --bin maw -- changes close --help."}	blake3:Bm9rQZPKSeoT6VL8xJrpZXi8mQ0oiLNOxxYFSSe9-yc
