1772760230386711	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEybw		item.comment	bn-36sh	{"body":"Implemented `maw changes pr <id>` idempotent lifecycle in crates/maw-cli/src/changes/mod.rs. Flow now: validate change metadata + local branch, push branch to origin, detect existing open PR by head/base via `gh pr list`, create PR if none (`gh pr create`, supports --draft/--title/--body-file/--fill), apply edits via `gh pr edit`, apply draft/ready toggles via `gh pr ready`/`--undo`, then persist PR metadata to change record store. Added text/json envelope output reporting created vs adopted behavior. Verified with cargo fmt, cargo test -p maw-cli changes_subcommand_is_registered, and cargo run -p maw-cli --bin maw -- changes pr --help."}	blake3:MFp80oP3K1YZnojJ5GQDc2_Fds4p4Z88D3Jh6d1dC7g
