1772760343163177	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEycw		item.comment	bn-394v	{"body":"Updated status output to be change-aware in crates/maw-cli/src/status.rs. `collect_status()` now reads active change records from .manifold/changes and surfaces them as structured items. Added Open changes section in text/pretty renderers, included `chgsets` in one-line output, and extended JSON envelope with `changes` + `open_changes`. Existing command outputs for implemented change subcommands already include explicit Next guidance. Verified with cargo fmt, cargo test -p maw-cli status -- --nocapture, and cargo run -p maw-cli --bin maw -- status --format text."}	blake3:WaIPl1D-6fFdO8yUUg4l33OGC-iU0GsCVOEIfKnoyLg
