1772760578697912	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEydQ		item.comment	bn-3bmt	{"body":"Implemented explicit source requirement for workspace creation. `maw ws create` now supports `--from` (alias `--revision`) and `--change`, with runtime enforcement that one must be provided for CLI usage. Updated create pipeline in crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/create.rs to resolve sources (workspace/branch/rev/remote), fetch only for remote-tracking sources, and bind workspace metadata to change ids. Added `change_id` to WorkspaceMetadata and wired workspace->change index/record updates via changes store when creating with --change. Updated internal restore/recover call sites for new create signature. Verified with cargo fmt, metadata tests, ws create help output, and a runtime check that ws create without source now fails with guidance."}	blake3:zHCcIDYeqqWREGe5qizyEdLn5yZQ0HSvtYizfZ31-Pg
