1772858810559836	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEysAE		item.comment	bn-beu5	{"body":"Field eval in fresh /tmp repos found four concrete regressions: (1) merge --into <change-id> advanced global epoch while main stayed behind, (2) stale/check/sync guidance contradicted itself for change workspaces, (3) maw push --advance could promote change-target work onto main, and (4) PREPARE snapshot failed on directory entries with 'Is a directory (os error 21)'. Child bones track fixes, regression tests, and help-text alignment."}	blake3:oGyxeqLEPVixsTTdo4DgtiPtHSDz292x79R47jieJcA
