1772923593355132	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEyvwE		item.create	bn-1bkj	{"description":"Repro from /tmp field eval: create change and merge into change target so epoch tracks change branch while main is behind; create unbound workspace from main; first maw exec auto-syncs workspace to current epoch (change head). Subsequent merge --into default can unintentionally carry active change commits to main. Expected: auto-sync/sync should refuse risky cross-target updates for unbound trunk workspaces when epoch tracks active change not yet on trunk. Acceptance: risky auto-sync skipped with actionable warning; sync --all also avoids these updates; no data loss.","kind":"bug","labels":["sync","changes-model","safety"],"parent":"bn-beu5","size":"l","title":"Prevent cross-target auto-sync from contaminating trunk workspaces"}	blake3:0C6FqTTndUZPuB_FzhYF13HpxtzjZUUABmUmy4hKAtA
1772923599641067	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEywAE		item.create	bn-vls4	{"description":"Even with push --advance guardrails, unbound workspaces can still carry active change commits and then be merged into default, promoting change-only history to trunk. Expected: merge --into default detects unbound source workspace HEAD that descends from active change branch not yet on target branch and refuses with clear remediation. Acceptance: merge blocked with actionable guidance; change-bound workspace flows remain valid.","kind":"bug","labels":["merge","safety","changes-model"],"parent":"bn-beu5","size":"m","title":"Block merge-into-default when unbound source includes active change ancestry"}	blake3:9GcVAmuGktRrhPARFhtw2duOPPujDG2vVWU6AQgM7nI
1772923607008749	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEywQE		item.create	bn-36iz	{"description":"Add integration regressions for: (1) maw exec auto-sync skipping risky unbound workspace when epoch tracks active change branch, and (2) merge --into default blocking unbound source workspace that already includes active change head not on trunk. Tests should fail pre-fix and pass post-fix.","kind":"task","labels":["testing","regressions","changes-model"],"parent":"bn-beu5","size":"m","title":"Add regressions for cross-target sync contamination and merge guardrails"}	blake3:SWIMVj6nYmoZFB4xwAgCAN0b3TrRQNSmS4vAZMRSL44
1772923983517644	1	itc:v3:AWKTMnkmSTJyZnQAAAAAQa2vVqtdbcAAAAEywgE		item.comment	bn-1bkj	{"body":"Implemented cross-target sync safety for unbound workspaces: when current epoch tracks an active change branch not yet on trunk, maw now refuses risky sync of trunk-based unbound workspaces (maw ws sync, maw ws sync --all skip entries, and auto-sync in maw exec). Added actionable warnings and preserved normal sync behavior for change-bound workspaces."}	blake3:vhCSTHcad04sONFHntHPkC_Iz9tqbqIq3pEN1ERkduQ
